metaTags.metaTitle: Cloudflare - The Web Performance & Security Company
metaTags.metaDescription: Here at Cloudflare, we make the Internet work the way it should. Offering CDN, DNS, DDoS protection and security, find out how we can help your site.

relatedBlades.title: A global network built for the cloud
relatedBlades.copy:
Cloudflare is a global network designed to make everything you connect to the Internet secure, private, fast, and reliable.

- Secure your websites, APIs, and Internet applications. 
- Protect corporate networks, employees, and devices. 
- Write and deploy code that runs on the network edge.

relatedBlades.title: Turn economic uncertainty into opportunity. Regain control with Cloudflare.

features.title: Cloudflare mitigates record-breaking DDoS attack
features.description: Cloudflare recently detected and mitigated dozens of hyper-volumetric DDoS attacks that peaked at 50-70 million requests per second (rps).

features.title: One year of war in Ukraine: Internet trends, attacks, and resilience
features.description: How Ukraine's Internet remained resilient in spite of dozens of disruptions in three different stages of the conflict.

features.title: Webinar: How Otrium thwarted a phishing attempt with Cloudflare
features.description: Learn how Otrium secured their almost-entirely-remote workforce against phishing attacks, and greatly reduced their attack surface.

addOns.entryTitle: HP - Main product category cards - SASE Cloudflare One
addOns.title: SASE - Cloudflare One

content.value: Zero Trust network-as-a-service platform to dynamically connect remote & on-site users to resources, with identity-based security controls.
Replace expensive, proprietary circuits with a single global network that provides built-in Zero Trust functionality, DDoS mitigation, network firewalling, and traffic acceleration.

relatedBlades.title: Need help getting started? Get a personalized recommendation.
Protect your Internet presence.
relatedBlades.copy:
Your website, APIs, and applications are your key channels for doing business with your customers and suppliers. As more and more shift online, ensuring these resources are secure, performant and reliable is a business imperative.

Cloudflare for Infrastructure is a complete solution to enable this for anything connected to the Internet.
